text: Tarundeep Rai is an Indian archer. He was born on 22 February 1984. Rai competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and 2020 Summer Olympics.Tarundeep RaiTarundeep RAI == References == Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Indian archers Category:Olympians for India
